Package: tsml.cara.rct
Type: Package
Title: Targeted Sequential Minimum Loss CARA RCT Design and Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2016-09-16
Authors@R: person("Antoine", "Chambaz", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="achambaz@u-paris10.fr")
Author: Antoine Chambaz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Antoine Chambaz <achambaz@u-paris10.fr>
Description: Simulation of a targeted sequential minimum loss covariate-adjusted response-adaptive (CARA) randomized clinical trial (RCT) design sampling and statistical inference of the average treatment effect or mean reward of the optimal treatment rule.
